    coiDeclaration: 'None',
    copyrightLicence: 'CC-BY',
    carriedOut: false,
    text: '<p>Terms initially searched a total of 108 articles. After we removed duplicates, checked the title and abstract, and reviewed full-text, eight studies&nbsp;3-10&nbsp;eventually met the predetermined inclusion and exclusion criteria. As of February 25, 2020, a total of4Journal Pre-proof46248 participants were included in our meta‐&nbsp;analysis. As presented in Table 1, the median age was 46.0 years and 23871 (51.6%) were men.</p><p><br></p><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700;">Table 1 Main Characteristics of included studies in the meta-analysis</span></p></div><table style="width: 100%;"><tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td>Study</td>\r\n\t<td>Date (Month, day)</td>\r\n\t<td colspan="2">Patients (no)</td>\r\n\t\r\n\t<td>Age (years)</td>\r\n\t<td colspan="4">Symptoms (%)</td>\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\t<td colspan="4">Comorbidities(%)</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td>All</td>\r\n\t<td>Male</td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td>Fever</td>\r\n\t<td>Cough</td>\r\n\t<td>Fatigue</td>\r\n\t<td>Dyspnoea</td>\r\n\t<td>Hypertension</td><td>Diabetes</td><td>Respiratory disorder</td><td>Cardiovascular disorder</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td>\r\n\t<td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n</div><br><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ArialMT;">a, average age; b, Meta-analysis for the prevalence was calculated from binary random-effects model analysis; c, The Novel Coronavirus Pneumonia Emergency Response Epidemiology Team</span></p></div></div><p><br></p>',
