    fundingStatement: 'This study received the following funding: Chinese Academy of Medical Sciences Innovation Fund for Medical Sciences (CIFMS 2018-I2M-1–003); National Science Grant for Distinguished Young Scholars (81425001/H0104); National Key Research and Development Program of China (2018YFC1200100, 2018YFC1200102); The Beijing Science and Technology Project (Z19110700660000); Major Projects of National Science and Technology on New Drug Creation and Development (2020ZX09201001). ',
    coiDeclaration: 'None',
